S.FORM: Cory Blackwell nalecuhan i Chicago, Illinois, nanu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. Seattle SuperSonics i 1984 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 2 ku uwac atu silsil 28, namapili' tu nu San Diego Rockets putiput. 3 bulad 27 demiad, 1963 a mihca, Cory Blackwell, miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
